{"tid":1938050,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國行緊三階段 三步曲？","createTime":"2020-03-22T09:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T09:44:06.000Z","uid":23174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"06f43a2a46a7aa1a606228811ced0c475b7ec714","tid":1938050,"uid":23174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-22T09:44:06.000Z","msg":"Copy from 某人<br />\n<br />\n第一階段: 配合國家宣傳-疫情受控, 民生逐步回復正常.<br />\n第二階段: 配合國家宣傳-受國際疫情影響,輸入個案大增,民生經濟大受衝擊.<br />\n第三階段: 配合國家劇本,一切都是外國勢力過錯,自己已經做得很好.大家要感恩,要以國家爲榮, 要以國家動員能力之强大自豪<br />\n<br />\n今日又睇到新聞<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516104-20200322.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516104-20200322.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=BTQ0Nb6fQhXLRDVXZ5xLdAmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=10c8a6f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1516104-20200322.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2ed037a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1516104-20200322.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n內地過去一日新增46宗新型肺炎確診病例，其中45宗是境外輸入病例，另1宗是與境外輸入有關聯的病例，來自廣東。國家衛健委新聞發言人米鋒表示，全國絕大多數地區已是低風險地區，要嚴防境外疫情輸入。"}]}